00:12:52,216 --> 00:12:54,506
and particle systems,
a lot of good stuff.


265
00:12:54,506 --> 00:12:58,626
And we're going to take a
look at each of these now.


266
00:12:58,676 --> 00:13:01,366
We'll start with the
base class, SKNode.


