00:40:24,946 --> 00:40:27,726
and I'm going to set
his collisionBitMask


875
00:40:28,466 --> 00:40:29,946
to be just BAD GUYS.


876
00:40:29,946 --> 00:40:31,446
I only want him to
collide with the baddies.


